ParameterFields.Name: SFX Type
ParameterFields.ToolTip: The SFX to play when it comes out of the ground. There's no noticeable difference between the two, so this is a useless parameter.

ParameterFields.Name: Sight Range (Tens)
ParameterFields.ToolTip: This number multiplied by 10 is used as a range within it notices Link and comes out of the ground. 255 will default to a range of 1000.

ParameterFields.Name: Enable Spawn Switch
ParameterFields.ToolTip: If this is not 0 or 255, the Dexivine will hide underground until this switch is set.
